873
00:37:35,160 --> 00:37:35,840
How is it still possible?

874
00:37:35,840 --> 00:37:36,840
We don't know who "killed" them.

875
00:37:36,840 --> 00:37:37,400
This matter—

876
00:37:38,880 --> 00:37:39,120
Me—

877
00:37:39,120 --> 00:37:39,680
He did it like this—

878
00:37:39,680 --> 00:37:40,680
The two of us went together.

879
00:37:40,680 --> 00:37:41,240
We got here.

880
00:37:41,240 --> 00:37:41,880
I didn't even look.

881
00:37:41,880 --> 00:37:43,320
Why am I holding a watermelon?

882
00:37:43,320 --> 00:37:44,400
Can't you go around?

883
00:37:44,400 --> 00:37:45,520
Go around to the back of the table.

884
00:37:49,640 --> 00:37:50,240
Scratch your head.

885
00:37:52,720 --> 00:37:53,800
Didn't expect that.

886
00:37:54,680 --> 00:37:55,760
Pretend to scratch your head.

887
00:37:58,800 --> 00:38:00,720
If I'd known, I'd have watched you eat.

888
00:38:05,040 --> 00:38:06,400
How many toothpicks are inside?

889
00:38:06,920 --> 00:38:07,400
Two.

890
00:38:08,760 --> 00:38:10,080
No, Sun Qian might be lying.

891
00:38:12,360 --> 00:38:13,360
She might not have eaten.

892
00:38:13,360 --> 00:38:14,800
She insists there are two inside.

893
00:38:15,200 --> 00:38:17,400
No one can give her two toothpicks now.

894
00:38:17,400 --> 00:38:18,880
Just vote her out and it's done.

895
00:38:18,880 --> 00:38:19,480
Aren't you—

896
00:38:19,480 --> 00:38:20,040
If you're worried—

897
00:38:20,040 --> 00:38:20,720
Why would you vote for me?

898
00:38:20,720 --> 00:38:21,840
What would I gain?

899
00:38:22,400 --> 00:38:24,120
Let's review it like this.

900
00:38:24,120 --> 00:38:25,480
An Yu ate here.

901
00:38:25,480 --> 00:38:26,520
No, I was the one who ate.

902
00:38:26,840 --> 00:38:28,280
Sun Qian was here.

903
00:38:29,240 --> 00:38:31,040
Then An Yu was "done for."

904
00:38:31,040 --> 00:38:32,160
Went back sulking.

905
00:38:32,160 --> 00:38:32,920
Sun Qian was here.

906
00:38:34,440 --> 00:38:35,680
I saw two toothpicks.

907
00:38:35,680 --> 00:38:36,360
But I called it out.

908
00:38:38,960 --> 00:38:39,960
So I voted for her.

909
00:38:41,320 --> 00:38:42,160
I think he "died" so—

910
00:38:42,160 --> 00:38:42,440
Openly and fairly.

911
00:38:42,440 --> 00:38:44,000
Just "died" so—just—

912
00:38:44,000 --> 00:38:44,480
How do I put it—

913
00:38:44,480 --> 00:38:45,120
Comfortably.

914
00:38:45,120 --> 00:38:46,360
He couldn't have that expression.

915
00:38:48,200 --> 00:38:49,800
He kept—

916
00:38:49,800 --> 00:38:50,400
Relaxed.

917
00:38:51,840 --> 00:38:52,920
Not even smiling.

918
00:38:53,280 --> 00:38:54,840
He looks so frustrated now, I think.

919
00:38:56,240 --> 00:38:57,000
Relaxed.

920
00:38:59,040 --> 00:39:00,680
You're a suspect now.

921
00:39:00,680 --> 00:39:01,480
Now there's suspicion.

922
00:39:01,480 --> 00:39:03,000
"Kill" someone so easy—

923
00:39:03,000 --> 00:39:04,800
A role that's easy to vote out.

924
00:39:13,800 --> 00:39:14,480
Sun Qian.

925
00:39:14,480 --> 00:39:16,560
If you can clarify this—

926
00:39:16,560 --> 00:39:17,600
If it's you, I won't vote for you.

927
00:39:20,960 --> 00:39:22,000
Come on, get ready—

928
00:39:22,000 --> 00:39:22,680
Get your move ready.

929
00:39:24,960 --> 00:39:26,200
I think the bag is Sun Qian's.

930
00:39:27,520 --> 00:39:28,920
I really don't think so.

931
00:39:28,920 --> 00:39:30,040
How many seasons have you carried?

932
00:39:30,040 --> 00:39:31,320
You keep carrying this and that.

933
00:39:33,360 --> 00:39:34,360
No, but this of hers—

934
00:39:34,360 --> 00:39:35,320
It's so illogical.

935
00:39:35,320 --> 00:39:36,960
She's totally illogical.

936
00:39:36,960 --> 00:39:38,160
A two-person start—

937
00:39:38,160 --> 00:39:39,360
I really believe she went.

938
00:39:39,360 --> 00:39:40,560
Didn't see anything.

939
00:39:43,640 --> 00:39:45,400
Why can't you believe this?

940
00:39:50,000 --> 00:39:51,680
That person is just smart.

941
00:39:56,880 --> 00:39:58,440
Try to recall again.

942
00:39:58,440 --> 00:39:59,280
Let me stand here and think.

943
00:39:59,280 --> 00:39:59,800
Right.

944
00:40:02,160 --> 00:40:03,320
Anyway, it's not this side.

945
00:40:03,320 --> 00:40:04,680
None of these people, anyway.

946
00:40:05,600 --> 00:40:07,720
Feels like it's these two or those two.

947
00:40:10,880 --> 00:40:11,360
These two.

948
00:40:12,160 --> 00:40:12,800
Us two.

949
00:40:18,960 --> 00:40:19,920
That one is also a good guy.

950
00:40:20,840 --> 00:40:21,800
How do you know?

951
00:40:21,800 --> 00:40:22,760
It's just a feeling, isn't it?

952
00:40:22,760 --> 00:40:24,360
Ask: Are you a good guy?

953
00:40:27,200 --> 00:40:27,720
Look at him—

954
00:40:27,720 --> 00:40:28,480
He admitted it, he—

955
00:40:30,280 --> 00:40:30,920
Just ask directly?

956
00:40:30,920 --> 00:40:31,920
Rely on honesty?

957
00:40:33,360 --> 00:40:34,160
Honesty.

958
00:40:34,440 --> 00:40:35,920
Can honesty move the werewolf?

959
00:40:36,640 --> 00:40:37,680
I've got an outside clue.

960
00:40:37,680 --> 00:40:38,440
I've got an outside clue.

961
00:40:41,600 --> 00:40:43,080
It's definitely this half.

962
00:40:45,440 --> 00:40:46,800
I'm sitting here with my legs crossed.

963
00:40:46,800 --> 00:40:48,000
That wolf is anxious.

964
00:40:48,320 --> 00:40:49,000
Come at me.

965
00:40:49,000 --> 00:40:50,440
Came over and did it to me.

966
00:40:52,400 --> 00:40:53,200
It's you.

967
00:40:54,200 --> 00:40:55,480
No wolf moved.

968
00:40:57,160 --> 00:40:58,800
How dumb is that?

969
00:40:59,600 --> 00:41:01,840
Then I have another outside clue.

970
00:41:06,360 --> 00:41:07,360
Just now, at the end when I opened my eyes—

971
00:41:07,360 --> 00:41:09,120
Jingyu seemed to slowly lower his hand.

972
00:41:12,520 --> 00:41:13,560
I'm calling it out.

973
00:41:13,560 --> 00:41:14,520
Everyone can open their eyes.

974
00:41:14,520 --> 00:41:15,800
Open eyes?

975
00:41:22,880 --> 00:41:23,800
We probably don't have—

976
00:41:23,800 --> 00:41:25,000
Raise your hand during meetings.

977
00:41:25,000 --> 00:41:26,120
This round, right?

978
00:41:28,840 --> 00:41:29,560
I'm really not.

979
00:41:29,560 --> 00:41:30,440
I swear I'm not.

980
00:41:36,400 --> 00:41:38,840
Why won't you even look me in the eye?

981
00:41:40,320 --> 00:41:41,400
Right now?

982
00:41:43,520 --> 00:41:44,240
You're the wolf.

983
00:41:46,280 --> 00:41:47,240
This is so much fun.

984
00:41:48,000 --> 00:41:48,840
Let's just vote now.

985
00:41:48,840 --> 00:41:50,680
Three, two, one—please vote.

986
00:41:55,600 --> 00:41:56,760
Who's number seven?

987
00:41:56,760 --> 00:41:57,600
You're seven.

988
00:41:59,440 --> 00:42:00,680
Who's number six?

989
00:42:02,960 --> 00:42:04,200
You.

990
00:42:05,840 --> 00:42:07,240
Vote for me.

991
00:42:07,240 --> 00:42:08,200
You're six.

992
00:42:08,200 --> 00:42:09,200
I'm six.

993
00:42:09,200 --> 00:42:09,840
Old Six.

994
00:42:09,840 --> 00:42:10,800
It's you, Old Six.

995
00:42:12,240 --> 00:42:13,120
I've cast my vote.

996
00:42:13,760 --> 00:42:14,720
Is it over?

997
00:42:14,720 --> 00:42:15,720
It's not over.

998
00:42:16,560 --> 00:42:17,160
See for yourself.

999
00:42:17,160 --> 00:42:17,720
You're the only one here.

1000
00:42:18,640 --> 00:42:19,400
I said we should vote for her.

1001
00:42:19,400 --> 00:42:19,920
Vote for her.

1002
00:42:19,920 --> 00:42:20,560
Why vote for me?

1003
00:42:20,560 --> 00:42:21,840
If you vote for me, I have to do this.

1004
00:42:23,200 --> 00:42:23,800
That was a mistake.

1005
00:42:23,800 --> 00:42:25,240
We should've sacrificed Sun Qian earlier.

1006
00:42:25,240 --> 00:42:26,920
Because she can't open her eyes, right?

1007
00:42:26,920 --> 00:42:28,080
She's a useless sheep now.

1008
00:42:29,200 --> 00:42:30,160
I'm nothing now.

1009
00:42:30,760 --> 00:42:32,440
Then we shouldn't have voted her out.

1010
00:42:32,440 --> 00:42:33,680
What are you talking about?

1011
00:42:35,680 --> 00:42:37,920
Next round, two of us should go again.

1012
00:42:37,920 --> 00:42:39,720
First, check if there are any toothpicks.

1013
00:42:39,720 --> 00:42:40,200
Right.

1014
00:42:40,200 --> 00:42:41,280
No, we don't have enough sheep.

1015
00:42:41,960 --> 00:42:43,720
Me and Chengcheng are useless sheep now.

1016
00:42:45,760 --> 00:42:48,400
We can only send one person each round.

1017
00:42:48,400 --> 00:42:51,000
All three sheep must get a toothpick.

1018
00:42:53,480 --> 00:42:54,400
Do you know the reason we're stuck now?

1019
00:42:54,400 --> 00:42:55,800
The only reason we're in this mess

1020
00:42:55,800 --> 00:42:57,040
is because you voted out

1021
00:42:57,040 --> 00:42:58,080
a capable sheep.

1022
00:42:58,080 --> 00:42:59,560
Just stand there like that.

1023
00:43:00,800 --> 00:43:02,560
Yeah, stop talking.

1024
00:43:06,480 --> 00:43:07,920
Everyone, please close your eyes.

1025
00:43:08,240 --> 00:43:09,280
Round three.

1026
00:43:09,640 --> 00:43:10,400
Darn it.

1027
00:43:10,800 --> 00:43:11,600
Are you going by yourself?

1028
00:43:12,120 --> 00:43:12,920
I'm going alone.

1029
00:43:25,000 --> 00:43:26,320
I think someone should watch him.

1030
00:43:26,320 --> 00:43:26,760
Yeah.

1031
00:43:26,760 --> 00:43:27,760
Keep an eye on him.

1032
00:43:58,400 --> 00:43:58,760
Brother Teng.

1033
00:43:58,760 --> 00:43:59,480
Brother Teng can't talk.

1034
00:43:59,480 --> 00:44:00,160
He can't make any moves.

1035
00:44:05,600 --> 00:44:07,400
Darn it, see, he can't talk now.

1036
00:44:07,400 --> 00:44:08,920
I got up earlier and watched, it was fine.

1037
00:44:13,760 --> 00:44:15,360
He can't even raise the alarm.

1038
00:44:16,000 --> 00:44:16,680
What's wrong?

1039
00:44:25,600 --> 00:44:26,640
I'm raising the alarm.

1040
00:44:29,360 --> 00:44:30,760
I have to raise the alarm now.

1041
00:44:35,040 --> 00:44:36,640
What was my original plan?

1042
00:44:36,640 --> 00:44:38,520
Because I suspected Brother Teng might be—

1043
00:44:38,520 --> 00:44:39,880
So I wanted to see what Brother Teng was doing.

1044
00:44:39,880 --> 00:44:41,040
I kept watching him.

1045
00:44:41,880 --> 00:44:43,640
Then Brother Teng walked over

1046
00:44:43,640 --> 00:44:45,040
After he got here,

1047
00:44:45,040 --> 00:44:47,280
he just stopped moving.

1048
00:44:47,280 --> 00:44:48,200
He just stood still here.

1049
00:44:48,200 --> 00:44:49,520
Then he saw me again.

1050
00:44:50,640 --> 00:44:51,480
He made this gesture to me.

1051
00:44:51,480 --> 00:44:52,600
Did you see it?

1052
00:44:52,600 --> 00:44:53,600
When I opened my eyes,

1053
00:44:53,600 --> 00:44:54,880
Brother Teng couldn't talk anymore.

1054
00:44:55,480 --> 00:44:56,440
It's already over.

1055
00:44:56,440 --> 00:44:57,800
Opened my eyes for nothing.

1056
00:44:57,800 --> 00:44:58,840
Your timing—

1057
00:44:58,840 --> 00:44:59,880
You're not even as good as

1058
00:44:59,880 --> 00:45:01,480
the one who just ate some watermelon.

1059
00:45:03,360 --> 00:45:04,080
No.

1060
00:45:05,160 --> 00:45:06,520
Also—

1061
00:45:06,520 --> 00:45:06,920
No.

1062
00:45:06,920 --> 00:45:08,120
But I still think it's a bit weird.

1063
00:45:08,120 --> 00:45:10,880
Because he got up without making a sound.

1064
00:45:10,880 --> 00:45:11,640
He said, "Darn it,"

1065
00:45:12,480 --> 00:45:14,200
and then snuck off.

1066
00:45:14,200 --> 00:45:15,080
It's just—me.

1067
00:45:16,240 --> 00:45:17,040
You.

1068
00:45:17,320 --> 00:45:18,200
I thought, since I wanted to go, we should—

1069
00:45:18,200 --> 00:45:19,080
You opened your eyes at that moment.

1070
00:45:19,080 --> 00:45:20,040
You were so sure.

1071
00:45:20,040 --> 00:45:21,160
That he'd go at that time.

1072
00:45:23,280 --> 00:45:24,880
Didn't even eat the watermelon.

1073
00:45:25,280 --> 00:45:26,880
Brother Teng gave me this sign.

1074
00:45:27,120 --> 00:45:28,160
He couldn't talk anymore.

1075
00:45:28,160 --> 00:45:29,280
Then you go eat.

1076
00:45:29,800 --> 00:45:30,960
Then raise the alarm again.

1077
00:45:32,560 --> 00:45:33,640
I can do that.

1078
00:45:34,800 --> 00:45:36,280
Did Brother Teng ask you—

1079
00:45:36,280 --> 00:45:38,240
"To kill me?"

1080
00:45:40,760 --> 00:45:41,320
You tell me.

1081
00:45:45,800 --> 00:45:46,800
And then you raised the alarm.

1082
00:45:48,040 --> 00:45:49,160
Is it possible—

1083
00:45:52,840 --> 00:45:54,040
Is it possible?

1084
00:45:54,040 --> 00:45:54,600
But I feel like—

1085
00:45:54,600 --> 00:45:56,160
There are just too many possibilities.

1086
00:45:56,160 --> 00:45:56,920
Feels like—

1087
00:45:57,320 --> 00:45:58,560
Look, Brother Bing hasn't said a word.

1088
00:45:58,560 --> 00:45:59,000
Is it possible—

1089
00:45:59,000 --> 00:46:00,480
Brother Bing actually knows everything.

1090
00:46:05,120 --> 00:46:06,240
Could it really be Brother Bing?

1091
00:46:09,640 --> 00:46:11,040
Brother Bing hasn't spoken at all.

1092
00:46:12,160 --> 00:46:14,000
I still don't get what this is.

1093
00:46:14,000 --> 00:46:15,160
What do you want me to say?

1094
00:46:15,640 --> 00:46:16,320
I think—

1095
00:46:17,080 --> 00:46:18,240
What I saw

1096
00:46:18,240 --> 00:46:19,520
I don't think it's Brother Bing.

1097
00:46:19,840 --> 00:46:20,920
It shouldn't be Brother Bing.

1098
00:46:24,360 --> 00:46:25,040
I am—

1099
00:46:25,040 --> 00:46:26,160
If it was Brother Bing,

1100
00:46:26,160 --> 00:46:27,920
Brother Teng should've turned toward me.

1101
00:46:30,040 --> 00:46:32,680
You can't figure this out.

1102
00:46:33,160 --> 00:46:33,840
Who to vote for?

1103
00:46:35,120 --> 00:46:36,240
Can I just cast a vote?

1104
00:46:40,920 --> 00:46:41,840
Please vote.

1105
00:46:43,000 --> 00:46:43,800
Xiaobai is already out.

1106
00:46:44,440 --> 00:46:46,720
Congratulations to the wolf for winning.

1107
00:46:51,800 --> 00:46:53,160
It's not Fan Chengcheng, right?

1108
00:46:53,160 --> 00:46:54,440
It's Xiaobai.

1109
00:46:54,440 --> 00:46:56,000
The winning wolf is Xiaobai.

1110
00:46:58,920 --> 00:46:59,920
What made the wolf strong this round

1111
00:46:59,920 --> 00:47:00,880
wasn't logic,

1112
00:47:00,880 --> 00:47:02,160
but timing.

1113
00:47:02,160 --> 00:47:03,720
The timing was perfect.

1114
00:47:07,160 --> 00:47:08,400
Thank you.

1115
00:47:10,040 --> 00:47:11,040
It really was Brother Bing.

1116
00:47:15,240 --> 00:47:17,280
See, no one suspected him.

1117
00:47:23,960 --> 00:47:25,160
Xiaobai is such a smart person.

1118
00:47:25,160 --> 00:47:25,920
Yibao.

1119
00:47:25,920 --> 00:47:27,280
It definitely can't be Bing.

1120
00:47:28,480 --> 00:47:29,920
Do you know that feeling of thrill?

1121
00:47:33,440 --> 00:47:34,960
It's driving me crazy holding it in.

1122
00:47:35,440 --> 00:47:36,600
Is this the all-knowing perspective?

1123
00:47:36,600 --> 00:47:37,440
This feels amazing.

1124
00:47:38,640 --> 00:47:39,680
Teng, can you describe

1125
00:47:39,680 --> 00:47:40,680
how you "died"?

1126
00:47:40,680 --> 00:47:41,600
Yeah, this—

1127
00:47:41,600 --> 00:47:42,040
Right.

1128
00:47:42,040 --> 00:47:43,960
How did Bai catch you—

1129
00:47:44,800 --> 00:47:45,280
No.

1130
00:47:47,520 --> 00:47:49,200
I thought Xiaobai "killed" me.

1131
00:47:50,160 --> 00:47:51,560
When I walked over here,

1132
00:47:51,560 --> 00:47:52,800
I said, let's see who opens their eyes.

1133
00:47:52,800 --> 00:47:53,920
I saw Xiaobai with his eyes open.

1134
00:47:55,280 --> 00:47:56,680
I said, open your eyes, open your eyes.

1135
00:47:56,920 --> 00:47:57,840
Yeah, and then I—

1136
00:47:57,840 --> 00:47:58,160
Right, I—

1137
00:47:58,160 --> 00:47:58,800
Darn it, look at me.

1138
00:47:59,320 --> 00:48:00,400
Darn it, Bing was behind me.

1139
00:48:05,120 --> 00:48:06,440
I didn't see.

1140
00:48:06,440 --> 00:48:07,560
Because I was like this—

1141
00:48:07,560 --> 00:48:08,400
I was watching Teng.

1142
00:48:08,400 --> 00:48:09,680
Teng was still with me.

1143
00:48:09,680 --> 00:48:11,040
He kept making me watch him.

1144
00:48:11,040 --> 00:48:11,840
So I just kept—

1145
00:48:11,840 --> 00:48:13,440
I said, watch him, watch him.

1146
00:48:13,440 --> 00:48:14,720
Suddenly, he stopped talking.

1147
00:48:14,720 --> 00:48:15,720
I could see such a wide area.

1148
00:48:15,720 --> 00:48:17,320
I didn't expect it to be over here.

1149
00:48:19,680 --> 00:48:21,360
Then can you tell me how you were

1150
00:48:21,360 --> 00:48:22,320
eliminated?

1151
00:48:22,320 --> 00:48:24,040
Sun Qian, three, two, one, open your eyes.

1152
00:48:24,880 --> 00:48:27,320
Go.

1153
00:48:27,840 --> 00:48:29,200
Turn around.

